    "en": {
      "title": "12 Indian fishermen freed",
      "author": "Vishnu",
      "body_lines": [
        "12 Indian fishermen who were arrested by the Sri Lankan Navy while engaged in illegal fishing have been released today by the Barutthurai Court on 08th Wednesday.",
        "12 Karaikal fishermen from Tamil Nadu were arrested by the Sri Lankan Navy last night on the 3rd of Jaffna."
      ],
